{"tid":1255881,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[有血腥圖，慎入]係俄羅斯既Oklhon Island 比狗咬 我問你答","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:55:45.000Z","uid":52238,"like":6,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"066052ea7d24c5b9e7490f577cf0262901354a38","tid":1255881,"uid":52238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"今日入咗Oklhon Island 諗住睇貝加爾湖<br />\n食完飯見有啲飽就去散下步<br />\n屌有隻類似狼狗咁既野行過見到我就沖埋嚟咬我<br />\n我明明淨係望咗佢一眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住個狗主帶咗我去醫院<br />\n醫院淨係拎消毒藥水消完毒就算<br />\n我問有冇瘋狗針打 佢地話呢到無 要出返Irkutsk 先有 <br />\n我而家最早都要聽日先返到去 仲要坐5個鐘車先出到去 <br />\n<br />\n個狗主聲稱佢隻狗有打疫苗 <br />\n個host 又聲稱呢個島無瘋狗症 啲人間中都會比狗咬都無野 <br />\n<br />\n屌 到底我中瘋狗症既機會大唔大 會唔會咁就英年早逝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面有傷口圖片 慎入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a91883d67ffd5860f180f845e15fd10430b4ac0","tid":1255881,"uid":216817,"like":31,"dislike":5,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:49:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"556ed5cfb3f291aaf9101af2803007c496b4881c","tid":1255881,"uid":85586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:52:48.000Z","msg":"你有無問佢主人係乜嘢令隻狗想咬你"},{"pid":"a453cd5a3510ca21364fe1defbc2dc5ae4218ade","tid":1255881,"uid":52238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"556ed5cfb3f291aaf9101af2803007c496b4881c","tid":1255881,"uid":85586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:52:48.000Z","msg":"你有無問佢主人係乜嘢令隻狗想咬你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:58:45.000Z","msg":"無問到阿，我個時係行過一見到佢，佢就沖過嚟咬我。"},{"pid":"ccf9ddd03ecc5b921108acd1b72e48a9c40c539b","tid":1255881,"uid":52238,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"7a91883d67ffd5860f180f845e15fd10430b4ac0","tid":12558