ets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97b6aa4df752abc3e58ff9860f02fa344e6a33c","tid":1255881,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:50:36.000Z","msg":"因為隻狗有瘋狗症，所以咬你"},{"pid":"b2bebd81ba741d055e92c9381703892bf797d443","tid":1255881,"uid":118351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:51:42.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯都有瘋狗症case,不過應該唔多,你唔洗咁擔心嘅<br />\n睇醫生問吓醫生話你洗唔洗打<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/hcp/vis/vis-statements/rabies.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fvaccines%2Fhcp%2Fvis%2Fvis-statements%2Frabies.html&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=c1a1e423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/hcp/vis/vis-statements/rabies.html</a><br />\n<br />\nVaccination after an exposure<br />\n<br />\nAnyone who has been bitten by an animal, or who otherwise may have been exposed to rabies, should clean the wound and see a doctor immediately. The doctor will determine if they need to be vaccinated.<br />\n<br />\nA person who is exposed and has never been vaccinated against rabies should get 4 doses of rabies vaccine &ndash; one dose right away, and additional doses on the 3rd, 7th, and 14th days. They should also get another shot called Rabies Immune Globulin at the same time as the first dose.<br />\n<br />\nA person who has been previously vaccinated should get 2 doses of rabies vaccine &ndash; one right away and another on the 3rd day. Rabies Immune Globulin is not needed."},{"pid":"2e05694acf0638a76da8f722334818e36b2e6769","tid":1255881,"uid":202348,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"煲咗佢隻狗嚟食<br />\n同狗主講你係大陸人"},{"pid":"bbf5c2da737b7546647dbced0ae854cec919085e","tid":1255881,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"066052ea7d24c5b9e7490f577cf0262901354a38","tid":1255881,"uid":52238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re